quran[11]{c,v,t}:
  45,27,"Ne obwaami bwomwikulu nende khushialo nibwa Nyasaye, ni inyanga yeyindukho olwa yiliula abonooni bakhasikhe"
  45,28,"Ne olilola buli omukanda nikusikame hasi, buli omukanda kulangwa okhutsia okhusoma eshitabu shiakwo, “lelo mularungwa kamwakholanga.”"
  45,29,"Eshitabu shiefu shino shiboola khwinywe khubwatoto, toto efwe khwahandikanga akamwakholanga"
  45,30,"Ne balia basuubila mana nibakhola amalayi , Nyasaye wabu Omulesi alibenjisia mutsimbabaasi tsitsie, okho nikho okhubura khwahabulafu"
  45,31,"Ne balia bakhaya baliboolelwa mbu: “ shimwasomelwakho tsinyaali tsianje mana nimuba nende obufuru mumioyo chienyu, mana nimuba Abandu bobwonooni.?”"
  45,32,"Ne olwa liliboolwa mbu: “ indache ya Nyasaye niyahabwene ne ebise bibula tsinganakani “nanyu nimuboola mbu: “khukorerwe indukho eyo, khuparirisinjiakhwo butwsa, ne khubula obwatoto.”"
  45,33,"Mana obubii bwabakhola bwakhabaloleshele, ne kalibabotokhana akabetseshelesinjia"
  45,34,"Baliboolelwa mbu: “olwalelo khubebilila shingala enywe mwebilila omukhung’ano kweyinyanga yenyu ino eshimenyo shienyu nimumulilo ne mubula ubahabina.”"
  45,35,Khulwo khuba enywe mwatseshelela tsinyaali tsia Nyasaye mana obulamu bwokhushialo nibubakatilisia. kholeelo shibalirusibwamwo tawe nohomba shibalileshelwa tawe
  45,36,"Oluyali nilwa Nyasaye Omulesi we likulu , Omulesi weshialo Omulesi webilonjo biosi"
  45,37,"Ne obukhongo ni obubwe butswa yenyene, mwikulu nende khushialo, naye ni owa Amaani Omuchesi muno"